extends java.lang.Object

Defines the three parameter types constants for JSON-RPC 2.0 requests and notifications.

  • NO_PARAMS The method takes no parameters
  • ARRAY The method parameters are packed as a JSON array e.g. ["val1", "val2", ...]
  • OBJECT The method parameters are packed as a JSON object e.g. {"param1":"val1", "param2":"val2", ...}
